data.actual_result: You will see the websites tooltip/pop-up appear on your screen while hovering your mouse in Discord.
data.expected_result: A URL pop-up/tooltip should not appear when you go back into Discord.
data.short_description: The URL will pop-up after going from a link to Discord with the **f3** key.**(MAC SPECIFIC)**
data.steps_to_repro: - Press f3. - Go from the browser window back to Discord. - Hover your mouse anywhere in Discord. - Watch for the URL pop-up to appear.
